Endif
Call ALICLCAMT([M:SOH4]ITMREF(NOL), [M]QTY(NOL), NOL, "SOH4", [M:SOH4]CLCAMT1(NOL), [M:SOH4]CLCAMT2(NOL)) From TRTX3
